  "detailed_description": "Jump back in time and free your inner caveman. Smash heads in this cooperative platformer game. Play solo or team up with up to 4 players. Inspired by games like <strong>New Super Mario</strong>, <strong>Joe & Mac</strong>, <strong>Metal Slug</strong>, <strong>Castle Crashers</strong> and <strong>Trine</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603420/extras/fcebcfcaa1d29dcb7d035a2542459fa4.avif?t=1771496892\" width=600 height=362 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603420/extras/2e094099e45e2bcf89fca92223e56881.avif?t=1771496892\" width=600 height=95 /></span><br>- <strong>Different playable characters</strong>: Choose one of the playable characters, but don’t worry! You can change your character at anytime in the game and play with them all!<br>- <strong>1-4 players</strong>: Play solo, with one, two or three friends. Work together to become unstoppable!<br>- <strong>Varied Enemies</strong>: Each level has different enemies, watch out as they can catch you unguarded.<br>- <strong>Secret Levels</strong>: Unlock secret levels inside the game for more excitement!<br>- <strong>Challenging</strong>: Challenge yourself to unlock all the achievements!",
  "about_the_game": "Jump back in time and free your inner caveman. Smash heads in this cooperative platformer game. Play solo or team up with up to 4 players. Inspired by games like <strong>New Super Mario</strong>, <strong>Joe & Mac</strong>, <strong>Metal Slug</strong>, <strong>Castle Crashers</strong> and <strong>Trine</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603420/extras/fcebcfcaa1d29dcb7d035a2542459fa4.avif?t=1771496892\" width=600 height=362 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603420/extras/2e094099e45e2bcf89fca92223e56881.avif?t=1771496892\" width=600 height=95 /></span><br>- <strong>Different playable characters</strong>: Choose one of the playable characters, but don’t worry! You can change your character at anytime in the game and play with them all!<br>- <strong>1-4 players</strong>: Play solo, with one, two or three friends. Work together to become unstoppable!<br>- <strong>Varied Enemies</strong>: Each level has different enemies, watch out as they can catch you unguarded.<br>- <strong>Secret Levels</strong>: Unlock secret levels inside the game for more excitement!<br>- <strong>Challenging</strong>: Challenge yourself to unlock all the achievements!",
